  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190540/extras/5c204daa8f3299b8eab0bf9aaf995a26.avif?t=1594677670\" width=500 height=100 /></span><br>Soona is a small 2d Side Scroller game that mainly focuses on melee keyboard controlled combat, and ranged combat to a lesser extent. The game starts at a specific point in a conflict that is out of context for the character at first, and your goal is to defeat soona and her allies, whether they are simple enemies, strange creatures, or bosses.<br><br><strong><u>Features</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190540/extras/d8f223008e65adb0585630b6a788b586.poster.avif?t=1594677670\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190540/extras/d8f223008e65adb0585630b6a788b586.webm?t=1594677670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190540/extras/d8f223008e65adb0585630b6a788b586.mp4?t=1594677670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Melee based combat and ranged attacks as support.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dangerous bosses.                                 </li></ul>                                                                                                                           <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enemy scenarios with obstacles.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2d handcrafted art.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190540/extras/2e511cd0a632a33cb8e5d517a7209881.avif?t=1594677670\" width=516 height=296 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190540/extras/33a23af95488d8aae8fc7de7289ff1fe.webp?t=1594677670\" width=600 height=50 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190540/extras/5c204daa8f3299b8eab0bf9aaf995a26.avif?t=1594677670\" width=500 height=100 /></span><br>Soona is a small 2d Side Scroller game that mainly focuses on melee keyboard controlled combat, and ranged combat to a lesser extent. The game starts at a specific point in a conflict that is out of context for the character at first, and your goal is to defeat soona and her allies, whether they are simple enemies, strange creatures, or bosses.<br><br><strong><u>Features</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190540/extras/d8f223008e65adb0585630b6a788b586.poster.avif?t=1594677670\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190540/extras/d8f223008e65adb0585630b6a788b586.webm?t=1594677670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190540/extras/d8f223008e65adb0585630b6a788b586.mp4?t=1594677670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Melee based combat and ranged attacks as support.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dangerous bosses.                                 </li></ul>                                                                                                                           <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enemy scenarios with obstacles.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2d handcrafted art.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190540/extras/2e511cd0a632a33cb8e5d517a7209881.avif?t=1594677670\" width=516 height=296 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor